body:
31 Days of Andi Mack

Day 2: What’s your favorite thing about being in the Friendom?

my favourite thing about being in this fandom is all the lovely and talented people! all the editors and artists and writers are so passionate about they do, and they share their gift with others, and it’s really amazing to see! everyone is very kind, and while we might get into fights over ships, and get a bit caught up in our theories, at the end of the day, we all have one thing in common: we love the show.

summary: Buffy Headcanons for Girls Week Day 2!
body:
Buffy Headcanons for Girls Week Day 2!

  • Okay so the one thing the slayer can’t ever seem to slay is ski ball. She is forever salty that it happens to be Cyrus’s natural skill
  • Buffy was one of those kids who dressed up in the same Halloween costume for like five years straight because they just idolized that one character so much
  • Buffy is chill with most bugs but she has a particular fear for the winged ones
  • fixes everything with duct tape
  • Her PowerPoint presentations are very aesthetically pleasing and organized
  • Even though she has -7393893 art skill, she makes an effort every year to give Andi and Cyrus homemade cards for their birthdays and it’s the sappiest you’ll ever see her
  • Dabs just to annoy Cyrus
  • very skilled at moving her eyebrows individually
  • “Let’s Rock Paper Scissors for it”
  • probably owns a secret diary
  • You’ll never see her nail polish on for more than a day
  • don’t ask on this one but I see her spontaneously breaking out into bohemian rhapsody often
  • Not even the GHC knows this but she can pogostick really well
  • Either immediately leaves group chats or never replies
  • The vine she quotes most often is the “I am disgusted. I am revolted. I-” etc
  • stays up late watching theories on shows she hasn’t watched and games she hasn’t played
  • has to look at the last page of a book before starting it
  • she’ll never admit to silently mouthing lyrics and doing the head bop™
  • if you call her when she’s tired, there’s a good chance she will fall asleep during it
  • Her guilty pleasure is F•R•I•E•N•D•S
  • Has the most stylish collection of sunglasses
  • “I’m totally failing this class right now” means she has a 93
  • She’s uhhhh como se dice queer

Okay, let’s talk about this. Remember when Cyrus was explaining that after his panic attack he went to the swings and that is where Buffy found him and she said “With TJ.”? Now remember how while saying this she looked at him exactly the same way she looked at him when she figured out he likes Jonah. Only this time Cyrus do not realize his feelings. 
Does this makes sence? Can we talk about how Buffy knows?
